Description
This is a program that shows basic information about the weather in any city on our planet.

Was used:
1) JavaFX - a library for linking code with a GUI
2) JSON - for reformatting weather data coming from an online service into data that is understandable for the client
3) SceneBuilder program - for creating a graphical interface and its design
4) IntellijIdea is a development environment for the Java programming language, all the code is written in it. The program starts from here.
